20th Road (O1d Bowery Bay Road), east from 31st Street, showing at
the left the Peter Rapelje farmhouse.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

725207f-b.text:

725208f-b.text:
(1)
31st Street, foreground, south of 20th Road (formerly Old Bowery Bay Road), showing the Peter Rapelje house from 1852-1873.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2 and 3)
The same, viewed westward, from 31st Street and showing also homes
on the west side in the background of 29th Street.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(4)
The same, showing the widening of 31st Street, looking north from Twenty-first Ave. (Wolcott Street). The site of the house was
at the left where the steam shovel is working.
May 28, 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
